$var reg 2 q, alu_op [1:0] $end
$var reg 1 I alu_src $end
$var reg 1 H branch $end
$var reg 1 D mem_read $end
$var reg 1 C mem_to_reg $end
$var reg 1 B mem_write $end
$var reg 1 > reg_write $end
$upscope $end
$scope module mem_wb_wall $end
$var wire 32 r, alu_result_in [31:0] $end
$var wire 1 ! clk $end
